": null, "solution": {"text": "<p>For dispersion without deviation</p><p><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><msub><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">&#948;</mi><mn>1</mn></msub><mo>+</mo><msub><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">&#948;</mi><mn>2</mn></msub><mo>=</mo><mn>0</mn></math></p><p><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mfenced><mrow><msub><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">&#956;</mi><mn>1</mn></msub><mo>-</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></mfenced><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">A</mi><msub><mo>&#8289;</mo><mn>1</mn></msub><mo>+</mo><mfenced><mrow><msub><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">&#956;</mi><mn>2</mn></msub><mo>-</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></mfenced><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">A</mi><msub><mo>&#8289;</mo><mn>2</mn></msub><mo>=</mo><mn>0</mn></math></p><p><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">A</mi><msub><mo>&#8289;</mo><mn>2</mn></msub><mo>=</mo><mo>-</mo><mfrac><mrow><mfenced><mrow><msub><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">&#956;</mi><mn>1</mn></msub><mo>-</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></mfenced><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">A</mi><msub><mo>&#8289;</mo><mn>1</mn></msub></mrow><mfenced><mrow><msub><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">&#956;</mi><mn>2</mn></msub><mo>-</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></mfenced></mfrac></math></p><p>Substituting the given values, we get</p><p><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">A</mi><msub><mo>&#8289;</mo><mn>2</mn></msub><mo>=</mo><mo>-</mo><mfrac><mrow><mfenced><mrow><mn>1</mn><mo>&#183;</mo><mn>5</mn><mo>-</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></mfenced><mn>5</mn><mo>&#176;</mo></mrow><mfenced><mrow><mn>1</mn><mo>&#183;</mo><mn>75</mn><mo>-</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></mfenced></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mo>-</mo><mfrac><mrow><mn>10</mn><mo>&#176;</mo></mrow><mn>3</mn></mfrac></math></p><p>The negative sign shows that the two prisms must be joined in opposition.</p>", "image": null}, "videoSolution": null, "numericalLowerLimit": null, "numericalUpperLimit": null, "cpyqbSubjects": ["61bb58181213731910ea0b70", "61c055eae8ce0dc8a5c62d33"